item.title: Bay Area Beogram 8002: Some cabinet work
item.description:
The Beogram 8002’s internal components are ready to be placed back into the cabinet, but the cabinet needs some attention first. While this Beogram’s cabinet is in good condition overall, there are a few things that need to be fixed, as mentioned in the initial assessment (linked in the original text). The first step was to remove the aluminum deck lid. The previous re-attachment used overly thick double-sided tape that created too much space...
